2
00:00:04,049 --> 00:00:06,349
<i>IN ORDER TO PROTECT HIS FRIEND,</i>

3
00:00:06,349 --> 00:00:11,216
<i>THE WARRIOR HAD TO TAKE</i>
<i>HIS FRIEND'S LIFE.</i>

4
00:00:11,216 --> 00:00:14,282
