5
00:00:14,282 --> 00:00:17,682
<i>THIS SWORD HAD CONTINUED</i>
<i>TO FIGHT FOR PEACE,</i>

6
00:00:17,682 --> 00:00:20,882
<i>YET REALIZED</i>
<i>THAT TO PROTECT THE PEACE,</i>

7
00:00:20,882 --> 00:00:24,649
