<i>THE ONE WHO WIELDED IT,</i>

8
00:00:24,649 --> 00:00:27,816
<i>AND THUS</i>
<i>TOOK ITS MASTER'S LIFE.</i>

9
00:00:27,816 --> 00:00:30,982
<i>THE WARRIOR AND THE SWORD</i>
<i>HAD TO DO WHAT THEY DID,</i>

10
00:00:30,982 --> 00:00:33,949
<i>BUT WAS THAT REALLY WHAT</i>
<i>THEY OUGHT TO HAVE DONE?</i>

11
00:00:33,949 --> 00:00:36,582
<i>UNCERTAIN OF THE ANSWER</i>
<i>EVEN NOW,</i>

12
