-HMM?

34
00:02:58,639 --> 00:03:01,573
[ THUD ]

35
00:03:01,573 --> 00:03:03,573
[ THUD ]

36
00:03:03,573 --> 00:03:06,539
-HER AGAIN.

37
00:03:09,606 --> 00:03:11,639
[ THUD ]

38
00:03:18,573 --> 00:03:21,106
-HMM. PERSISTENT GIRL.

39
00:03:21,106 --> 00:03:22,573
-FAKIR?

40
00:03:22,573 --> 00:03:23,873
-SO YOU'RE AWAKE.

41
00:03:23,873 --> 00:03:25,873
-WHERE'S TUTU?

42
00:03:25,873 --> 00:03:29,306
-DON'T WORRY.
TUTU IS LONG GONE.

43
00:03:29,306 --> 00:03:32,239
WHAT HAPPENED?

44
00:03:32,239 --> 00:03:34,673
-TUTU HELPED ME.

45
00:03:34,673 --> 00:03:36,006
-HMM?

46
00:03:36,006 --> 00:03:39,339
-SHE TRIED TO RESTORE
PART OF MY HEART TO ME.

47
00:03:39,339 --> 00:03:41,639
-MYTHO, YOU KNOW --

48
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:43,806
-THAT'S WHEN KRAEHE CAME.

49
00:03:43,806 --> 00:03:45,706
-KRAEHE?
-YES.

50
00:03:45,706 --> 00:03:47,473
SHE WAS DRESSED LIKE
A BLACK BIRD

51
00:03:47,473 --> 00:03:50,639
AND SHE TOOK THE PIECE.

52
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:54,139
TELL ME, FAKIR, WOULDN'T IT...

53
00:03:54,139 --> 00:03:55,973
WOULDN'T IT BE BETTER FOR ME

54
00:03:55,973 --> 00:03:59,139
