OF MY HEART?

55
00:03:59,139 --> 00:04:00,439
-FORGET ABOUT IT.

56
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,639
-BUT...

57
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:04,173
-LISTEN TO ME,
I BROUGHT YOU BACK HERE

58
00:04:04,173 --> 00:04:07,873
BECAUSE I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE
SAFER TO HAVE PEOPLE AROUND.

59
00:04:07,873 --> 00:04:11,373
BURY YOUR WORRIES IN SLEEP.

60
00:04:11,373 --> 00:04:15,106
[ SIGHS ]

61
00:04:15,106 --> 00:04:18,373
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

62
00:04:18,373 --> 00:04:23,973
[ SIGHS ]

63
00:04:23,973 --> 00:04:25,506
[ MOANS ]

64
00:04:31,906 --> 00:04:35,573
-WHAT...WHAT IS THIS?

65
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:40,139
[ GASPS ]
-WHY?

66
00:04:40,139 --> 00:04:41,806
-WHO'S THERE?

67
00:04:41,806 --> 00:04:44,139
-WHY DID YOU BRING ME
BACK WITH YOU?

68
00:04:44,139 --> 00:04:45,973
-ARE YOU MYTHO'S...

69
00:04:45,973 --> 00:04:48,639
I-I BROUGHT YOU WITH ME?
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

70
00:04:48,639 --> 00:04:49,806
-[ CHUCKLES ]

71
00:04:49,806 --> 00:04:51,906
YOU WANT TO KNOW A LOT,
DON'T YOU?

72
00:04:51,906 --> 00:04:53,773
I KNOW HOW YOU FEEL

73
00:04:53,773 --> 00:04:56,139
BECAUSE I HAVE THE DESIRE
FOR KNOWLEDGE.

74
00:04:56,139 --> 00:04:57,573
-DESIRE FOR KNOWLEDGE?

75
00:04:57,573 --> 00:05:00,473
-YOU DON'T REMEMBER
HOW YOU BROUGHT ME HERE?

76
00:05:00,473 --> 00:05:02,373
-I-I BROUGHT YOU?

77
00:05:02,373 --> 00:05:03,639
YOU'RE LYING.

78
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:05,706
-WHY DO YOU DON BLACK FEATHERS?

79
00:05:05,706 --> 00:05:06,873
-[ GASPS ]

80
00:05:06,873 --> 00:05:08,273
NO!

81
00:05:08,273 --> 00:05:10,439
-DO YOU HAVE A SPECIAL POWER
DWELLING WITHIN YOU?

82
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:14,339
COME ON, TELL ME.
WHICH ONE IS THE REAL YOU?

83
00:05:14,339 --> 00:05:15,673
-STOP IT.

84
00:05:15,673 --> 00:05:16,839
-WHO ARE YOU, REALLY?

85
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:18,706
-STOP!

86
00:05:23,239 --> 00:05:24,406
[ OPENS DRAWER ]

87
00:05:24,406 --> 00:05:25,639
[ BOX THUDS ]

88
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,806
[ SLAMS DRAWER ]

89
00:05:26,806 --> 00:05:29,606
[ BREATHES HEAVILY ]

90
00:05:36,306 --> 00:05:37,473
-I SAW YOU!
-HUH?

91
00:05:37,473 --> 00:05:38,806
-I SAW YOU FOR SURE!

92
00:05:38,806 --> 00:05:41,773
[ Muffled screaming ]

93
00:05:41,773 --> 00:05:43,873
-CONFESSING YOUR LOVE
AT THE WINDOW?

94
00:05:43,873 --> 00:05:45,439
DUCK, YOU'RE SO BOLD!

95
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,539
-WHAT?

96
00:05:46,539 --> 00:05:48,573
-IT WAS LIKE A REVERSE
ROMEO AND JULIET,

97
00:05:48,573 --> 00:05:51,773
BUT HORRIBLY DIFFERENT
IN THAT IT WAS SO ONE-SIDED.

98
00:05:51,773 --> 00:05:55,073
-NO, THAT'S NOT IT.
MYTHO DISAPPEARED, AND I --

99
00:05:55,073 --> 00:05:56,673
-RIGHT! I FORGOT!

100
00:05:56,673 --> 00:05:58,939
HE HASN'T BEEN TO CLASS
IN A LONG TIME, HUH?

101
00:05:58,939 --> 00:06:00,439
-THAT'S WHY YOU COULDN'T
CONTAIN YOURSELF

102
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:02,073
AND RESOLVED TO CONFESS.

103
00:06:02,073 --> 00:06:03,739
-NO, IT ISN'T!

104
00:06:03,739 --> 00:06:06,506
-TAKE THIS CHANCE
TO ATTACK, ATTACK, ATTACK!

105
00:06:06,506 --> 00:06:08,806
-THOUGH YOU REALLY HAVE NO HELP
SINCE THE WONDERFUL MYTHO

106
00:06:08,806 --> 00:06:10,939
ALREADY HAS RUE.

107
00:06:10,939 --> 00:06:12,573
-GO FOR IT! TAKE YOUR LOSSES.

108
00:06:12,573 --> 00:06:14,039
-LOSE AND BE CRUSHED!

109
00:06:14,039 --> 00:06:15,673
-BUT -- BUT I WAS JUST --

110
00:06:15,673 --> 00:06:17,473
-HE MIGHT SHOW UP
FOR CLASS TODAY!

111
00:06:17,473 --> 00:06:19,039
-WHAT? YOU THINK SO?

112
00:06:19,039 --> 00:06:21,506
-YOU'RE HOPEFUL, AREN'T YOU?
THAT'S SO CUTE!

113
00:06:21,506 --> 00:06:24,606
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

114
00:06:24,606 --> 00:06:26,339
-WILL MYTHO COME TODAY?

115
00:06:26,339 --> 00:06:28,606
-IF HE DOES, YOU HAVE TO SAY IT
LOUD AND CLEAR!

116
00:06:28,606 --> 00:06:30,173
-HUH? SAY WHAT?

117
00:06:30,173 --> 00:06:31,239
-OH, COME ON, DUCK. WHAT ELSE?
-OH, COME ON, DUCK. WHAT ELSE?

118
00:06:31,239 --> 00:06:32,373
-HUH?

119
00:06:32,373 --> 00:06:33,573
-THAT YOU LOVE HIM!
-THAT YOU LOVE HIM!

120
00:06:33,573 --> 00:06:36,473
-WHAT?!
I CAN'T TELL HIM THAT BECAUSE...

121
00:06:36,473 --> 00:06:39,339
<i>[ Thinking ] BECAUSE IF I SAID</i>
<i>THAT, I'D VANISH.</i>

122
00:06:39,339 --> 00:06:40,573
-OH, YOU COULD!
-[ SCREAMS ]

123
00:06:40,573 --> 00:06:41,806
-WAIT, WHERE'S SHE GOING?

124
00:06:41,806 --> 00:06:44,206
-IT WAS YOUR FAULT!
-NO WAY!

125
00:06:44,206 --> 00:06:45,973
-[ GASP ]
-[ SQUEALS ]

126
00:06:45,973 --> 00:06:47,906
-[ GROANS ]

127
00:06:47,906 --> 00:06:49,939
-DUCK?
-HUH?

128
00:06:51,906 --> 00:06:53,173
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

129
00:06:53,173 --> 00:06:55,573
-[ GASPS ] MYTHO!

130
00:06:57,106 --> 00:07:00,839
-YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

131
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:03,339
I'M SO GLAD!

132
00:07:03,339 --> 00:07:04,806
-[ SCREAMING ]

133
00:07:07,039 --> 00:07:08,573
-[ SCREAMS ]

134
00:07:08,573 --> 00:07:09,906
I'M SORRY, I'M SO SORRY!

135
00:07:09,906 --> 00:07:11,706
I LOOKED ALL OVER TOWN
BUT I COULDN'T FIND YOU

136
00:07:11,706 --> 00:07:13,506
SO I WAS WONDERING
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU.

137
00:07:13,506 --> 00:07:15,939
AND NOW SEEING YOU'RE OKAY,
IT'S SUCH A RELIEF AND I-I --

138
00:07:15,939 --> 00:07:18,906
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]

139
00:07:18,906 --> 00:07:21,506
I'M JUST GLAD THAT YOU'RE OKAY.

140
00:07:21,506 --> 00:07:23,873
-YOU WERE LOOKING FOR ME?

141
00:07:23,873 --> 00:07:27,939
<i>-[ Thinking ] OH! THAT'S RIGHT.</i>
<i>HE DOESN'T KNOW I'M TUTU, SO...</i>

142
00:07:27,939 --> 00:07:30,239
-HUH? TUTU?
-UH...

143
00:07:30,239 --> 00:07:32,273
-DO YOU KNOW ABOUT TUTU, DUCK?

144
00:07:32,273 --> 00:07:34,506
-UH, UM, WELL...

145
00:07:34,506 --> 00:07:35,673
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

146
00:07:38,173 --> 00:07:39,473
-FAKIR!

147
00:07:42,073 --> 00:07:45,939
-MYTHO, YOU GO AHEAD.
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

148
00:07:45,939 --> 00:07:48,073
-YES.

149
00:07:48,073 --> 00:07:51,373
-[ Whimpers ]

150
00:07:51,373 --> 00:07:53,939
-NOW YOU...
-[ GASPS ] YES?

151
00:07:53,939 --> 00:07:56,406
[ Whimpers ]

152
00:07:57,939 --> 00:07:59,839
-YOU'RE SUCH AN EYESORE.

153
00:07:59,839 --> 00:08:03,839
LISTEN CAREFULLY --
NEVER COME NEAR MYTHO AGAIN.

154
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:07,339
IF YOU DO, I'LL MAKE SURE
YOU PAY FOR IT.

155
00:08:07,339 --> 00:08:09,073
[ Whimpers ]

156
00:08:14,373 --> 00:08:18,873
[ Whimpering ]

157
00:08:18,873 --> 00:08:22,239
-SO, WHAT WAS THE OUTCOME?
DOES THIS MEAN SHE FAILED?

158
00:08:22,239 --> 00:08:24,506
-IT WAS A RATHER SUBDUED
LETDOWN.

159
00:08:24,506 --> 00:08:26,839
BUT WE'LL SET A REVENGE MATCH
FOR HER.

160
00:08:29,473 --> 00:08:30,973
<i>-[ Thinking ] LAST NIGHT,</i>

161
00:08:30,973 --> 00:08:34,973
<i>I SAW TUTU RETURN A PIECE</i>
<i>OF MYTHO'S HEART TO HIM.</i>

162
00:08:34,973 --> 00:08:37,239
<i>MYTHO ALSO WISHED</i>
<i>FOR ITS RETURN.</i>

163
00:08:37,239 --> 00:08:40,739
<i>THEN...I SAW THAT,</i>

164
00:08:40,739 --> 00:08:42,873
<i>AND AFTER THAT,</i>

165
00:08:42,873 --> 00:08:44,239
<i>WHAT...</i>

166
00:08:44,239 --> 00:08:46,739
<i>WHO -- WHO AM I?</i>

167
00:08:46,739 --> 00:08:49,239
[ BELL TOLLS ]

168
00:08:49,239 --> 00:08:51,139
-[ SIGHS ]

169
00:08:51,139 --> 00:08:53,839
<i>[ Thinking ] I SKIPPED</i>
<i>ALL MY MORNING CLASSES.</i>

170
00:08:53,839 --> 00:08:56,506
<i>[ SIGHS ]</i>

171
00:08:56,506 --> 00:08:59,006
<i>FAKIR HAD THAT SCARY LOOK</i>
<i>IN HIS EYES.</i>

172
00:08:59,006 --> 00:09:01,706
<i>MYTHO SHOULDN'T BE WITH</i>
<i>SOMEONE LIKE THAT.</i>

173
00:09:01,706 --> 00:09:03,439
<i>BUT WHAT SHOULD I DO?</i>

174
00:09:03,439 --> 00:09:07,106
[ MUSIC PLAYING ]

175
00:09:07,106 --> 00:09:09,073
-OH, HELLO, MISS EDEL.

176
00:09:09,073 --> 00:09:10,739
-YES, HELLO, DUCK.

177
00:09:10,739 --> 00:09:14,739
-MISS EDEL, I NEED SOME HELP.

178
00:09:14,739 --> 00:09:16,306
I WANNA SAVE MYTHO FROM FAKIR,

179
00:09:16,306 --> 00:09:18,239
BUT FAKIR TOLD ME NOT
TO GO NEAR MYTHO

180
00:09:18,239 --> 00:09:19,673
OR ELSE HE'D MAKE ME PAY FOR IT.

181
00:09:19,673 --> 00:09:23,739
WHICH KIND OF SCARES ME,
BUT, I MEAN, I RATHER...

182
00:09:23,739 --> 00:09:26,173
HUH?

183
00:09:26,173 --> 00:09:28,473
-THE NAME OF THIS GEM
IS "COURAGE,"

184
00:09:28,473 --> 00:09:30,673
A SINGLE GEM MADE OF TWO.

185
00:09:30,673 --> 00:09:33,006
<i>-[ Thinking ]</i>
<i>A SINGLE GEM MADE OF TWO.</i>

186
00:09:33,006 --> 00:09:35,806
<i>DOES THAT MEAN I SHOULD</i>
<i>WORK TOGETHER WITH SOMEONE?</i>

187
00:09:35,806 --> 00:09:38,506
<i>BUT WHO?</i>

188
00:09:38,506 --> 00:09:41,839
<i>I CAN'T PUT RUE IN DANGER.</i>

189
00:09:41,839 --> 00:09:43,606
<i>[ GASPS ]</i>

190
00:09:43,606 --> 00:09:46,873
-I WANT YOU
TO RESTORE MY HEART, TUTU.

191
00:09:46,873 --> 00:09:51,306
<i>-[ Thinking ] IF -- IF I LET</i>
<i>MYTHO KNOW THAT I'M TUTU,</i>

192
00:09:51,306 --> 00:09:55,639
<i>THEN TOGETHER, WE MIGHT BE ABLE</i>
<i>TO STAND UP TO FAKIR.</i>

193
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:56,906
-FAKIR?

194
00:09:56,906 --> 00:09:59,139
WHAT IS FAKIR TO YOU, DUCK?

195
00:09:59,139 --> 00:10:03,606
-HUH? WHAT IS HE?
NOTHING REALLY TO ME,

196
00:10:03,606 --> 00:10:07,039
BUT HE'S A DANGEROUS PERSON
TO MYTHO.

197
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,139
OH!

198
00:10:08,139 --> 00:10:10,539
WHAT?

199
00:10:10,539 --> 00:10:12,306
MISS EDEL!

200
00:10:12,306 --> 00:10:15,739
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

201
00:10:15,739 --> 00:10:17,506
-QUACK! QUACK, QUACK, QUACK.

202
00:10:21,006 --> 00:10:23,739
<i>-[ Thinking ] ALL RIGHT.</i>

203
00:10:23,739 --> 00:10:27,906
[ SNIFFING ]

204
00:10:27,906 --> 00:10:29,339
<i>THIS IS IT!</i>

205
00:10:29,339 --> 00:10:32,906
<i>NO DOUBT ABOUT IT.</i>
<i>IT'S MYTHO'S SMELL!</i>

206
00:10:32,906 --> 00:10:34,739
QUACK, QUACK, QUACK, QUACK!

207
00:10:34,739 --> 00:10:37,839
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

208
00:10:37,839 --> 00:10:39,073
[ GASPS ]

209
00:10:39,073 --> 00:10:40,606
<i>[ Thinking ]</i>
<i>OH, NO! SOMEONE'S COMING!</i>

210
00:10:40,606 --> 00:10:41,973
QUACK, QUACK!

211
00:10:45,006 --> 00:10:46,573
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

212
00:10:46,573 --> 00:10:48,873
<i>- [ Thinking ] AN IGUANA?</i>

213
00:10:48,873 --> 00:10:49,973
[ SIGHS ]

214
00:10:49,973 --> 00:10:50,973
<i>THAT WAS CLOSE.</i>

215
00:10:50,973 --> 00:10:52,006
[ DOOR OPENS ]

216
00:10:54,239 --> 00:10:58,973
-QUACK! [ GROANING ]

217
00:11:00,506 --> 00:11:02,706
<i>[ Thinking ] WH -- WHAT? WHAT?!</i>

218
00:11:09,973 --> 00:11:11,973
-THERE.

219
00:11:11,973 --> 00:11:14,006
YOU'RE SO STUPID.

220
00:11:14,006 --> 00:11:18,473
THERE'S NO WAY YOU WERE
GOING TO FIND ANY FOOD IN THERE.

221
00:11:18,473 --> 00:11:19,773
[ CHUCKLES ]

222
00:11:19,773 --> 00:11:21,973
I GUESS YOU WOULDN'T HAVE
WANDERED IN IF YOU KNEW.

223
00:11:21,973 --> 00:11:24,673
-QUA -- QUACK, QUACK, QUACK,
QUACK, QUACK.

224
00:11:24,673 --> 00:11:25,706
-[ LAUGHS ]

225
00:11:25,706 --> 00:11:30,173
YOU SURE EAT A LOT.
HURRY HOME.

226
00:11:30,173 --> 00:11:32,206
DON'T COME AROUND ANYMORE.

227
00:11:32,206 --> 00:11:36,939
<i>-[ Thinking ] SOMEHOW,</i>
<i>HE WASN'T LIKE THE USUAL FAKIR.</i>

228
00:11:36,939 --> 00:11:39,939
-IF YOU DO, I'LL MAKE SURE
YOU PAY FOR IT.

229
00:11:39,939 --> 00:11:41,939
<i>-[ Thinking ]</i>
<i>NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO!</i>

230
00:11:41,939 --> 00:11:44,239
<i>HE'S DEFINITELY A BAD GUY.</i>

231
00:11:44,239 --> 00:11:46,806
<i>I'M NOT GONNA BE FOOLED JUST</i>
<i>BECAUSE THE BREAD WAS TASTY.</i>

232
00:11:46,806 --> 00:11:50,173
<i>HE PROBABLY ACTED LIKE THAT</i>
<i>ONLY BECAUSE I WAS JUST A DUCK.</i>

233
00:11:50,173 --> 00:11:51,673
<i>A DUCK?</i>

234
00:11:51,673 --> 00:11:53,639
<i>IF I'M GONNA TELL MYTHO</i>
<i>EVERYTHING,</i>

235
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:55,739
<i>I BETTER TELL HIM</i>
<i>THAT I'M JUST A DUCK, TOO,</i>

236
00:11:55,739 --> 00:11:57,439
<i>SHOULDN'T I?</i>

237
00:11:57,439 --> 00:12:00,939
QUACK, QUACK, QUACK.

238
00:12:00,939 --> 00:12:03,973
[ TCHAIKOVSKY'S "DANCE OF
THE SUGAR PLUM FAIRY" PLAYING ]

239
00:12:14,982 --> 00:12:16,982
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

240
00:12:16,982 --> 00:12:18,982
-WHAT'S THAT?

241
00:12:18,982 --> 00:12:22,982
-DUCK SAYS SHE HAS SOMETHING
IMPORTANT TO TELL ME.

242
00:12:22,982 --> 00:12:24,916
<i>-"I'LL BE WAITING</i>
<i>IN THE SCHOOL'S BACKYARD</i>

243
00:12:24,916 --> 00:12:27,016
<i>AT 5:00 THIS EVENING. DUCK."</i>

244
00:12:27,016 --> 00:12:30,049
-DID THAT GIRL NOT HEAR
WHAT I SAID TO HER?

245
00:12:30,049 --> 00:12:33,549
[ SCOFFS ] THROW IT AWAY.
THERE'S NO NEED TO GO.

246
00:12:33,549 --> 00:12:35,182
-NO.

247
00:12:35,182 --> 00:12:36,316
-WHAT?

248
00:12:36,316 --> 00:12:39,282
-I'VE CHOSEN TO GO, FAKIR.

249
00:12:39,282 --> 00:12:42,282
-YOU'RE KIDDING, RIGHT?

250
00:12:42,282 --> 00:12:43,349
-I MEAN IT.

251
00:12:43,349 --> 00:12:44,682
-WHAT POINT IS THERE?

252
00:12:44,682 --> 00:12:47,516
-MAYBE THERE'S SOMETHING
SHE CAN TELL ME ABOUT TUTU.

253
00:12:47,516 --> 00:12:48,982
-WHO? DUCK?
-YES.

254
00:12:48,982 --> 00:12:51,082
-MORON.
THERE'S NO WAY SHE COULD KNOW.

255
00:12:51,082 --> 00:12:53,782
-BUT --
-DON'T GET INVOLVED WITH TUTU.

256
00:12:53,782 --> 00:12:56,716
HER EXISTENCE WILL JUST BRING
YOU UNHAPPINESS IN THE END.

257
00:12:56,716 --> 00:12:58,549
DON'T BE FOOLED.
-HUH?

258
00:12:58,549 --> 00:13:00,516
-AND ON TOP OF THAT,
YOU HAVE THAT KRAEHE

259
00:13:00,516 --> 00:13:02,182
CHASING AFTER YOU RIGHT NOW.

260
00:13:02,182 --> 00:13:03,382
-I DON'T CARE.

261
00:13:03,382 --> 00:13:06,149
-IF I TELL YOU, "NO," IT'S NO!
YOU GOT THAT?

262
00:13:06,149 --> 00:13:08,082
-NO.

263
00:13:08,082 --> 00:13:09,316
[ SLAPS ]
-THAT'S ENOUGH FROM YOU!

264
00:13:09,316 --> 00:13:11,316
-OH, MY GOSH.
-HE SLAPPED HIM.

265
00:13:13,082 --> 00:13:14,949
-I'M SORRY.

266
00:13:16,582 --> 00:13:19,449
-I <i>AM</i> GOING.

267
00:13:22,049 --> 00:13:23,482
-[ GROANS ]

268
00:13:23,482 --> 00:13:27,082
SO I'M NO LONGER ABLE
TO STOP MYTHO WITH WORDS.

269
00:13:27,082 --> 00:13:29,082
[ RUNNING FOOTSTEPS ]

270
00:13:29,082 --> 00:13:30,549
-[ PANTING ]

271
00:13:45,182 --> 00:13:48,216
[ FOOTSTEPS DESCENDING ]

272
00:14:09,682 --> 00:14:11,382
<i>-UH-OH.</i>

273
00:14:11,382 --> 00:14:16,016
<i>THAT IS THE PRINCE'S OWN SWORD,</i>
<i>WHICH ONCE SHATTERED HIS HEART.</i>

274
00:14:16,016 --> 00:14:18,916
<i>NOW WHAT DO YOU PLAN</i>
<i>TO DO WITH IT?</i>

275
00:14:18,916 --> 00:14:22,849
<i>[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]</i>

276
00:14:22,849 --> 00:14:25,882
-[ SPEAKING GERMAN ]

277
00:14:29,382 --> 00:14:32,382
[ SWORD ZINGS ]

278
00:14:51,649 --> 00:14:53,516
[ SWORD SLASHES ]

279
00:14:53,516 --> 00:14:55,549
[ SHATTERS ]

280
00:15:02,582 --> 00:15:04,116
-MYTHO.

281
00:15:07,516 --> 00:15:11,016
[ INHALES DEEPLY,
EXHALES SLOWLY ]

282
00:15:11,016 --> 00:15:12,582
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]
-OH.

283
00:15:12,582 --> 00:15:15,916
[ GASPS ]

284
00:15:15,916 --> 00:15:19,016
I-E-I-E-I...O.
-HUH?

285
00:15:19,016 --> 00:15:20,716
-IS THAT DUCK?

286
00:15:20,716 --> 00:15:24,382
-UM, I-I, UH, ACTUALLY,
ACTUALLY...

287
00:15:24,382 --> 00:15:26,049
DO, DO, DO, DO.

288
00:15:26,049 --> 00:15:27,182
-TUTU.

289
00:15:27,182 --> 00:15:29,782
-HUH? NO WAY.
YOU KNEW ALL ALONG?

290
00:15:29,782 --> 00:15:32,249
-YOU KNOW ABOUT TUTU,
DON'T YOU, DUCK?

291
00:15:32,249 --> 00:15:35,716
-HUH? OHH. YOU SCARED ME.

292
00:15:35,716 --> 00:15:38,049
-FAKIR TOLD ME THAT
I SHOULDN'T COME HERE, BUT...

293
00:15:38,049 --> 00:15:41,349
-YOU TOLD FAKIR ABOUT THIS?

294
00:15:41,349 --> 00:15:43,049
-YES.
-[ GROANS ]

295
00:15:43,049 --> 00:15:44,482
<i>[ Thinking ] RIGHT.</i>

296
00:15:44,482 --> 00:15:46,982
<i>EVERYTHING I TELL MYTHO</i>
<i>GOES STRAIGHT TO FAKIR, TOO.</i>

297
00:15:46,982 --> 00:15:48,549
-DUCK.
-YES?

298
00:15:48,549 --> 00:15:51,049
-I-I WANT TO SEE TUTU.

299
00:15:51,049 --> 00:15:52,549
-HUH?

300
00:15:52,549 --> 00:15:54,482
-WHENEVER I THINK OF TUTU,

301
00:15:54,482 --> 00:15:57,482
I BECOME FILLED WITH
THE DESIRE TO SEE HER.

302
00:15:57,482 --> 00:15:58,849
-MYTHO...

303
00:15:58,849 --> 00:16:01,816
-I WANT TO BE WITH TUTU ALWAYS.

304
00:16:10,349 --> 00:16:11,349
[ WINGS FLUTTER ]

305
00:16:11,349 --> 00:16:12,349
-[ GASPS ]

306
00:16:12,349 --> 00:16:15,449
[ SCREAMS, GROANS ]

307
00:16:25,082 --> 00:16:28,049
-MY PRINCE, YOU BELONG TO ME.

308
00:16:30,082 --> 00:16:32,149
-KRAEHE?

309
00:16:32,149 --> 00:16:35,416
-[ LAUGHS ] THAT'S RIGHT!
THAT'S THE SPIRIT!

310
00:16:35,416 --> 00:16:38,982
THE VALUE OF TREASURE IS
REVEALED WHEN IT'S FOUGHT OVER.

311
00:16:38,982 --> 00:16:42,749
NOW, WHICH DESERVING MAID
WILL THE PRINCE WANT TO GO TO,

312
00:16:42,749 --> 00:16:45,049
MY DEAR PRINCESS TUTU?

313
00:16:47,049 --> 00:16:48,349
[ BUBBLING ]

314
00:16:48,349 --> 00:16:53,382
[ TINKLING ]

315
00:16:53,382 --> 00:16:56,049
[ BUBBLING ]

316
00:16:56,049 --> 00:16:57,149
[ DING ]

317
00:16:59,982 --> 00:17:03,982
-YOUR HAIR, YOUR CHEEKS,
EVEN YOUR HEART.

318
00:17:03,982 --> 00:17:05,916
EVERYTHING BELONGS TO ME.

319
00:17:05,916 --> 00:17:06,982
-PLEASE, STOP.

320
00:17:06,982 --> 00:17:08,282
KRAEHE.

321
00:17:08,282 --> 00:17:10,082
-PRINCESS TUTU.

322
00:17:10,082 --> 00:17:11,982
-RETURN THE HEART SHARD
YOU TOOK.

323
00:17:11,982 --> 00:17:15,149
STOP MAKING THE PRINCE SUFFER.
-TUTU...

324
00:17:15,149 --> 00:17:17,782
-I'M TREMBLING.

325
00:17:17,782 --> 00:17:19,049
LOOK, MY PRINCE,

326
00:17:19,049 --> 00:17:21,982
THERE'S THE ONE MAKING YOU
SUFFER -- PRINCESS TUTU.

327
00:17:21,982 --> 00:17:22,982
-WHAT?

328
00:17:22,982 --> 00:17:24,216
-NO!

329
00:17:24,216 --> 00:17:25,716
NO, THAT'S A LIE!

330
00:17:25,716 --> 00:17:30,382
-MY POOR PRINCE,
I'M THE ONE YOU NEED.

331
00:17:30,382 --> 00:17:32,416
I ALONE.

332
00:17:32,416 --> 00:17:35,349
I WILL ALWAYS BE WITH YOU.

333
00:17:35,349 --> 00:17:36,949
-KRAEHE.

334
00:17:36,949 --> 00:17:40,516
-YOU'RE LIKE A DOLL,
BUT I WILL LOVE YOU.

335
00:17:40,516 --> 00:17:44,249
I WILL MAKE YOU FORGET TUTU.

336
00:17:44,249 --> 00:17:46,916
WE'LL JUST GIVE THESE
HEART THINGS TO THE CROWS.

337
00:17:46,916 --> 00:17:48,182
-[ GASPS ] NO!

338
00:17:48,182 --> 00:17:50,682
[ RAVENS CAWING ]

339
00:17:50,682 --> 00:17:53,873
[ WIND GUSTS ]

340
00:17:57,773 --> 00:18:00,413
[ SWORD ZINGS ]

341
00:18:00,413 --> 00:18:02,280
-THAT'S THE PRINCE'S SWORD.

342
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:04,247
-SO, YOU'RE KRAEHE?

343
00:18:04,247 --> 00:18:06,213
-HOW DARE YOU ADDRESS ME, FILTH!

344
00:18:06,213 --> 00:18:08,513
-ARE YOU THE RAVEN'S MANIFEST?

345
00:18:08,513 --> 00:18:12,247
[ GROANS ]

346
00:18:12,247 --> 00:18:14,180
[ FABRIC RIPS,
OBJECT CLATTERS ]

347
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,647
[ WINGS FLUTTER ]

348
00:18:15,647 --> 00:18:18,347
-WHO AM I SUPPOSED TO BE?

349
00:18:20,313 --> 00:18:21,380
[ SHATTERS ]

350
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:24,247
-THE SHARD!
-IT'S NO USE...

351
00:18:24,247 --> 00:18:25,947
PRINCESS TUTU.

352
00:18:25,947 --> 00:18:28,947
-WHO ARE...

353
00:18:28,947 --> 00:18:30,947
[ ARMOR CLATTERS ]

354
00:18:30,947 --> 00:18:32,613
-FAKIR!

355
00:18:32,613 --> 00:18:34,780
-SORRY YOU'VE HAD TO WAIT,
MYTHO.

356
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:37,613
IT'S ALL RIGHT NOW.
YOU WON'T HAVE TO SUFFER.

357
00:18:37,613 --> 00:18:38,913
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

358
00:18:38,913 --> 00:18:40,780
-SIT DOWN.

359
00:18:40,780 --> 00:18:42,213
I'LL SET THINGS RIGHT.

360
00:18:42,213 --> 00:18:44,780
I WILL SHATTER YOUR HEART
FOR YOU ONCE AGAIN.

361
00:18:44,780 --> 00:18:45,947
-WHAT?!

362
00:18:45,947 --> 00:18:48,680
-AND YOU WILL NOT STOP ME,
PRINCESS TUTU!

363
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:51,447
-MYTHO!

364
00:18:51,447 --> 00:18:54,447
YOU, FAKIR? YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO SHATTERED MYTHO'S HEART?

365
00:18:54,447 --> 00:18:56,780
WHY'D YOU DO
SUCH AN AWFUL THING?

366
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:59,447
[ TCHAIKOVSKY'S
"FANTASY OVERTURE" PLAYING ]

367
00:18:59,447 --> 00:19:00,947
-IF YOU HAD NOT SHOWN UP,

368
00:19:00,947 --> 00:19:02,947
THEN NONE OF THIS
WOULD'VE HAPPENED.

369
00:19:02,947 --> 00:19:04,447
-I...

370
00:19:04,447 --> 00:19:06,413
-TUTU...

371
00:19:09,747 --> 00:19:12,480
-[ GROANS ]
-[ GASPS ]

372
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:13,747
-FAKIR, STOP IT!

373
00:19:13,747 --> 00:19:15,180
-PRINCE!

374
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:17,913
[ SWORD CLATTERS ]

375
00:19:17,913 --> 00:19:19,313
-[ GASPS ]

376
00:19:23,147 --> 00:19:24,347
-IS IT MY FAULT?

377
00:19:24,347 --> 00:19:27,013
IF I PIERCED MY HEART
WITH THIS SWORD,

378
00:19:27,013 --> 00:19:29,247
WILL THAT SATISFY YOU, FAKIR?

379
00:19:29,247 --> 00:19:32,813
-THAT'S RIGHT. THEN YOU'LL
RETURN TO YOUR OLD SELF.

380
00:19:32,813 --> 00:19:34,747
-ALL RIGHT.
-WHAT?

381
00:19:34,747 --> 00:19:36,213
[ SWORD CLANGS ]

382
00:19:38,247 --> 00:19:40,247
-[ GASPS ] MYTHO!

383
00:19:40,247 --> 00:19:42,013
DON'T DO IT!

384
00:19:42,013 --> 00:19:43,713
MYTHO!

385
00:19:43,713 --> 00:19:46,213
YOU'D RATHER BE
WITHOUT A HEART?!

386
00:19:46,213 --> 00:19:48,713
-DO IT! QUICKLY!
PIECE YOUR HEART!

387
00:19:48,713 --> 00:19:50,847
-MYTHO, PLEASE, DON'T!

388
00:19:50,847 --> 00:19:52,947
NO! NO!
-DO IT NOW.

389
00:19:52,947 --> 00:19:54,713
DO IT!
-NO!

390
00:19:54,713 --> 00:19:58,213
THE OTHER DAY YOU SMILED,
REMEMBER?

391
00:19:58,213 --> 00:20:02,280
WHEN I SAW THAT, I THOUGHT,
THIS MUST BE THE REAL YOU.

392
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,847
I BELIEVE IF YOUR HEART
IS FULLY RESTORED

393
00:20:04,847 --> 00:20:07,513
THEN YOU'D BE ABLE TO SHOW
EVEN MORE OF YOURSELF

394
00:20:07,513 --> 00:20:09,747
BECAUSE THAT'S THE REAL YOU!

395
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:15,247
[ CRYING ]

396
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:18,847
I'M SORRY.

397
00:20:18,847 --> 00:20:20,847
[ TINKLES ]

398
00:20:20,847 --> 00:20:24,280
[ CRYING ]

399
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:29,447
I CAN'T SAVE OR PROTECT YOU
FROM THE SUFFERING.

400
00:20:29,447 --> 00:20:32,847
BECAUSE ALL I CAN DO
IS RESTORE YOUR HEART TO YOU.

401
00:20:32,847 --> 00:20:34,280
THAT'S IT.

402
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:38,013
[ CRYING ]

403
00:20:38,013 --> 00:20:40,013
[ SWORD CLANGS ]

404
00:20:40,013 --> 00:20:42,513
-MYTHO.

405
00:20:42,513 --> 00:20:44,313
-I SEE.

406
00:20:44,313 --> 00:20:47,513
SO THIS IS THE ANSWER
YOU HAVE CHOSEN.

407
00:20:54,513 --> 00:20:58,413
-TUTU, RESTORE THIS HEART SHARD
TO ME.

408
00:21:00,313 --> 00:21:01,880
[ GASPS ]

409
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:04,747
AAH!

410
00:21:04,747 --> 00:21:07,547
OH.

411
00:21:07,547 --> 00:21:09,213
PRINCESS TUTU.

412
00:21:13,247 --> 00:21:15,447
I WANT TO KNOW...
-HUH?

413
00:21:21,747 --> 00:21:24,480
-WHAT DO YOU THINK OF ME?

414
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:26,613
I WANT TO KNOW.

415
00:21:26,613 --> 00:21:28,280
-I...

416
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:31,247
UH, I...

417
00:21:31,247 --> 00:21:34,713
-WAIT. TUTU.

418
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:39,080
WHY ARE YOU RUNNING, TUTU?

419
00:21:40,613 --> 00:21:42,580
<i>-[ Thinking ] I'M A DUCK.</i>

420
00:21:42,580 --> 00:21:45,080
<i>I'M REALLY ONLY A BIRD.</i>

421
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:47,747
<i>BUT WHAT THE PRINCE SEES</i>
<i>IS PRINCESS TUTU</i>

422
00:21:47,747 --> 00:21:50,080
<i>IN HER BEAUTIFUL DRESS.</i>

423
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:51,713
<i>IT'S NOT ME.</i>

424
00:21:51,713 --> 00:21:54,413
[ BELL TOLLING ]
<i>-WAS WHAT THE SWORD PIERCED</i>

425
00:21:54,413 --> 00:21:56,113
<i>THE PRINCE'S HEART?</i>

426
00:21:56,113 --> 00:21:58,680
<i>OR WAS IT SOMEONE'S FEELINGS?</i>

427
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:03,713
<i>[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]</i>

428
00:22:03,713 --> 00:22:06,747
[ RITSUKO OKAZAKI'S "ALTHOUGH
MY LOVE IS SMALL" PLAYING ]

429
00:22:16,547 --> 00:22:18,380
<i>-♪ YUME MIRU ♪</i>

430
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:20,980
<i>♪ YOU NI ♪</i>

431
00:22:20,980 --> 00:22:23,480
<i>♪ KOI O SHITA NO ♪</i>

432
00:22:26,847 --> 00:22:29,413
<i>♪ FUKURAMU ♪</i>

433
00:22:29,413 --> 00:22:34,413
<i>♪ KOKORO GA FUKURAMU NO YO ♪</i>

434
00:22:34,413 --> 00:22:39,080
<i>♪ IKITERUTTE SUTEKI</i>
<i>NA KOTO TO OMOTTA ♪</i>

435
00:22:41,713 --> 00:22:46,413
<i>♪ ASU GA MACHI DOOSHII ♪</i>

436
00:22:46,413 --> 00:22:48,313
<i>♪ MM ♪</i>

437
00:22:48,313 --> 00:22:55,313
<i>♪ ANATA NO CHIKARA NI NARITAI</i>
<i>NO DONNA TOKI NI MO WATASHI ♪</i>

438
00:22:55,313 --> 00:22:59,413
<i>♪ MATTE MATTE</i>
<i>KURENAI HASHITTE ♪</i>

439
00:22:59,413 --> 00:23:01,880
<i>♪ HASHITTE IKU NO YO ♪</i>

440
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:08,013
<i>♪ KAZE MO AMAGUMO</i>
<i>MO OIKOSHITE ♪</i>

441
00:23:08,013 --> 00:23:15,247
<i>♪ WATASHI DAKE</i>
<i>NO TSUBASA HABATAITE ♪</i>

442
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:37,113
-I <i>AM</i> RUE.

443
00:23:37,113 --> 00:23:38,847
I'M NOT ANYONE ELSE.

444
00:23:38,847 --> 00:23:40,247
THAT'S WHO I'VE ALWAYS BEEN.

445
00:23:40,247 --> 00:23:42,613
-RUE, MAYBE I'M ACTUALLY...

446
00:23:42,613 --> 00:23:45,713
-ONCE AGAIN,
PRINCESS TUTU WILL CHANGE MYTHO.

447
00:23:45,713 --> 00:23:48,080
-KRAEHE,
WHY ARE YOU IN SUCH PAIN?

448
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:50,547
-BEGONE, YOU UGLY CROW.

449
00:23:50,547 --> 00:23:52,013
-THAT'S RIGHT. I <i>AM</i> A CROW.

450
00:23:52,013 --> 00:23:54,413
AND I, ALONE,
AM THE TRUE PRIMA DONNA,

451
00:23:54,413 --> 00:23:56,647
PRINCESS KRAEHE.

452
00:23:56,647 --> 00:24:00,080
-ALL WHO LOVE STORIES,
GATHER 'ROUND.

453
00:24:00,080 --> 00:24:03,580
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

